Installation instructions:
==================
Place the .bsp file in C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\<your account name>\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

Notes:
==================

Some of the highlights of this jailbreak map include:

- An alarm room with monitors
- A solitary that slides into the ground
- A visiting room, medic, kitchen / cafeteria, pool, shower, disco, armory, and cell block area
- A torture room

And more!

Please leave a comment if you have any criticism or suggestions - I could really use it!

Have fun!
